Sooooooooo recently I’ve been trying to learn how to record myself! Usually I’m not tech savvy and I really don’t get into other peoples lanes. I’m that artists that JUST likes writing, singing, rapping, and performing. I feel like engineers are magicians and truly deserve so much credit in making music. TRUTH IS…. 

I’ve always felt like a stepping stone. Always the giver of love and never the getter…. Sometimes there’s a glimpse of hope. Then i remember who I am and just how rare I can be. This sounds bleak and sad lol but it’s still a very full life! Cuz see, what I’ve learned is that love isn’t about receiving… it’s simply giving. Giving your best, giving your all, giving your heart, giving your joy, giving what someone else needs! Whether your needs are met or not. Just like God! God loves us unconditionally… even when we fall short! Even when we fail. Even when we don’t realize we need him or respect and love him the way he deserves. God loves us anyway! That’s how I love. I have God within me… through and through! And yes, it sucks sometimes BUT it’s all I know. I have my fears in love and I’m super resistant in so many ways. But I couldn’t stop loving if I tried. And trust me, I’ve tried!!! 

So this one is to the girls that love hard and real!! To the girls that always give everything they’ve got and just haven’t found the person who returns it. Just know, you’re not alone. You’re needed in this world! The same love you give others, be sure to give yourself! Cuz we deserve it… 

#love #Loveyourself #UnconditionalLove #God #GodBody #GodLike

JULY RECAP!!! 🎉🎉🎉

Now that August is here… let me give y’all a little July Recap!

I didn’t do a birthday post this year… my bday was July 9th! 

I decided this month that I was gonna live it up for my bday and just be on GO!!! And that’s just what i did! 

Started the month in Cancun and got to witness my amazing cousin marry his amazing wife! ❤️ 
My girls joined me and we had a time! 

Ride bikes and bust my ass 🥴 

Went to Fort Lauderdale for a lil vacay and sweet treat! Got cute and relaxed. 

Went to LA and performed at @hardrockla ❤️ Had a billboard and EVERYTHING!!! 🤗 
Spent some time with my favorites 🥰 

Went to the spa twice! Just relaxing and maxing!!! 

Worked on some musical content! 🤞🏾❤️‍🔥

Went to Miami to end the month off on a high note and had a BLAST! 
From pool parties to yachts to jet skiing and eating like a fatty! 

Shout out to all involved who played a role in making this bday month lit. I love you all dearly! 🥰😘❤️‍🔥🫶🏾🤞🏾

July was EVERYTHING! I liiivveeedddd!!! 

It’s time to get back to the grind and I couldn’t be more anxious about my next steps. 

PRAYING FOR A PROSPEROUS YEAR!! May God play favorites with me…. 🙏🏾
